<div class="font-serif text-lg text-[#6B1D2A]">The Clinical Curator</div>
<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8">
<a class="font-sans Inter text-sm tracking-wide text-[#2C2C2C]/60 dark:text-[#E2DCD2]/60 hover:text-[#6B1D2A] transition-colors" href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
<a class="font-sans Inter text-sm tracking-wide text-[#2C2C2C]/60 dark:text-[#E2DCD2]/60 hover:text-[#6B1D2A] transition-colors" href="#">Terms of Service</a>
<a class="font-sans Inter text-sm tracking-wide text-[#2C2C2C]/60 dark:text-[#E2DCD2]/60 hover:text-[#6B1D2A] transition-colors" href="#">Clinical Standards</a>
<a class="font-sans Inter text-sm tracking-wide text-[#2C2C2C]/60 dark:text-[#E2DCD2]/60 hover:text-[#6B1D2A] transition-colors" href="#">Contact</a>
